{"id": "art-226", "label": "Art. 226", "title": "Art. 226", "slug": "art-226", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 226 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Asociatul în societatea în nume colectiv,\nîn comandit&#259; simpl&#259; sau în societatea cu r&#259;spundere\nlimitat&#259; se poate retrage din societate:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)în\ncazurile prev&#259;zute în actul constitutiv;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1938780923\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1904\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1938780923\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a<sup>1</sup>)în cazurile prev&#259;zute la art. 134;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)cu\nacordul tuturor <span class=SpellE>celorlal&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_682016241\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1903\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_682016241\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)în lipsa unor prevederi în actul constitutiv sau când nu\nse realizeaz&#259; acordul unanim asociatul se poate retrage pentru motive\ntemeinice, în baza unei hot&#259;râri a tribunalului, supus&#259; numai\napelului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1676992454\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1902\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1676992454\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)Dreptul de retragere poate fi exercitat, în\ncazurile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. a) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nb), în termen de 30 de zile de la data public&#259;rii hot&#259;rârii\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> în\nMonitorul Oficial al României, Partea a IV-a. <span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. 134 alin. (2<sup>1</sup>) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)În <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) lit. c), <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\njudec&#259;toreasc&#259; va dispune, prin <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span>\nhot&#259;râre, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu privire la structura\nparticip&#259;rii la capitalul social a <span class=SpellE>celorlal&#355;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1403754443\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1901\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1403754443\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Drepturile asociatului retras, cuvenite pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sale sociale, se stabilesc prin acordul <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> ori de un expert desemnat de <span\nclass=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span> sau, în caz de <span class=SpellE>neîn&#355;elegere</span>,\nde tribunal. Costurile de evaluare vor fi suportate de societate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>TITLUL <span class=SpellE>VI:Dizolvarea</span>,\nfuziunea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> divizarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL I:Dizolvarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span></span></b></p>"}